{"tid":1843301,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[封關否則醫護罷工] 九星連珠外憂內患踐踏中国大好時機","createTime":"2020-01-26T06:50:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T10:19:29.000Z","uid":249563,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"de855a653f243057e5a47fc0ef4152afbf91683c","tid":1843301,"uid":249563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T06:50:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支那先有美國貿易戰<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">節節敗退</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">武漢肺炎確診個案過千 賤種數量減少</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">全世界都知你無好帶歇</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點狠狠踐踏呢班蝗蟲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1.繼續打破温層 </span></span><br />\n班<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">港豬</span></strong>都上口罩同share新聞、文宣既時候<br />\n全民人人自危 大家最關心新聞既時刻<br />\n重啟instagram、<strong>whatsapp</strong>、<strong>Twitter</strong> 戰線 話俾佢知政府有幾賣港 港共置港人於險境 重推<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我要真普選</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">2.繼續塑造本土意識</span></span><br />\n推黃色經濟圈之餘 被忽略既<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">重點係你罷食幾多間你以前會食既藍店、藍日用品</span></strong> 推崇<span style=\"color: red;\">中國貨就係垃圾同無良產物</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />能唔能夠遵循全憑自律 罷政府年宵係個好開始 要塑造到喺街拎住藍店既購物袋都要畏首畏尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />炒口罩、同藍絲有瓜葛等店、人士我地有專業清算師 靜伺時機<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大原則 <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">敵疲我追</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好俾呢班仆街回血黎危害我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">封關否則醫護罷工</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddf4aa6e31caad51564a30efd68271902b5df5b0","tid":1843301,"uid":249563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T06:51:47.000Z","msg":"港豬都識上口罩保命 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c106d113c0a04e159b3a96a24ee47b566042bf48","tid":1843301,"uid":249563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T06:52:48.000Z","msg":"港共有成億口罩囤積居奇<br />\n危害港人 仲乞中央俾黑心口罩我地"},{"pid":"951cded9894ea92f7d61078b9d3f2d2bf0eb2218","tid":1843301,"uid":249563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T06:53:42.000Z","msg":"沒有同情別人的資格<br />\n何況班中國人係應有既報應"},{"pid":"3e09c9c70ecef4c154349ce951af0f9b2f9b8026","tid":1843301,"uid":249563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T06:54:21.000Z","msg":"封關否則醫護罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fb3ba11a289bfa4407bb1ea00e03fbfe8c4d49f","tid":1843301,"uid":249563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T06:55:28.000Z","msg":"停課淨係停中小學 <br />\n擺明分化年輕人<br />\n佢地就唔理政治港豬育成<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96333b4526946f79766502d11f5ea041cd04d621","tid":1843301,"uid":249563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T07:10:05.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"273b05cd383c5234ffd48f280416e4dac4c9605d","tid":1843301,"uid":249563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T07:10:17.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"3ccd06ca398d60291d1afc253b